> I recently checked out an old issue of Home Education

We just started getting Boomerang. We've gotten three so far. My
five year old loves it and listens to them over and over. She
already loved stories and books on tape. I like to listen to
Boomerang, too, so it's great for the car. I'm not sure what the
age range is for it.
